Fetching: The process of grabbing data from the db and making it available to the application.
- Fetching too much data adds overhead in terms of both JDBC communication and ResultSet processing.
- Fetching too little data might cause additional fetching to be needed.

FetchType: defines whether Hibernate will load data eagerly or lazily 决定是否延迟获取
- static 支持EAGER或者LAZY两种模式(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
- dynamic

FetchMode: how Hibernate will fetch the data 决定如何获取(获取的方式)
- FetchMode.SELECT    适用额外的Select查询语句来获取数据
- FetchMode.SUBSELECT 将Select查询语句放到同一个Select的where查询条件中
- FetchMode.JOIN      适用join来查询关联的表
- @LazyCollection

